OL,3,CMohamed Salah says he will always love
OL,4,CLiverpool as nine-year story nears an
OL,5,Cend
OL,7,FLiverpool forward Mohamed Salah
OL,8,Finsists he will always love the club
OL,9,Fas he prepares to bid farewell after
OL,10,Fnine years.
OL,12,FThis season has been the most
OL,13,Ffrustrating and unhappiest of his
OL,14,Ftenure at Anfield, in which he won the
OL,15,FChampions League and two Premier
OL,16,FLeague titles as well as four Golden
OL,17,FBoots, and that has been reflected in
OL,18,Fsome of his public comments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
