OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779696396
OL,3,CMohamed Salah says he will always love
OL,4,CLiverpool as nine-year story nears an
OL,5,Cend
OL,7,FIn December he was dropped from the
OL,8,Fsquad after claiming he had been
OL,9,F"thrown under the bus" after being
OL,10,Fbenched after a run of poor results
OL,11,Ffor the team and he also said his
OL,12,Frelationship with head coach Arne Slot
OL,13,Fhad broken down.
OL,15,FThat was patched up enough for him to
OL,16,Freturn to the team after the Africa
OL,17,FCup of Nations but the mutual decision
OL,18,Fto part ways with a year of his
OL,19,Fcontract still remaining suggested it
OL,20,Fwas only a temporary truce.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]
