OL,3,CMohamed Salah says he will always love
OL,4,CLiverpool as nine-year story nears an
OL,5,Cend
OL,7,FHis social media post after last
OL,8,Fweek's defeat at Aston Villa, calling
OL,9,Ffor a return to the "heavy metal
OL,10,Ffootball" of the Jurgen Klopp era may
OL,11,Fhave resonated with fans but it did
OL,12,Flittle to convince observers he and
OL,13,FSlot see eye to eye.
OL,15,FBut as his final day at the club
OL,16,Fapproaches with the visit of Brentford
OL,17,Fon Sunday Salah spoke about his
OL,18,Ffeelings for the Liverpool and its
OL,19,Fsupporters.
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
