OL,3,CMohamed Salah says he will always love
OL,4,CLiverpool as nine-year story nears an
OL,5,Cend
OL,7,F"The club means everything. The people
OL,8,Fmean everything, the city means
OL,9,Feverything. I will always love this
OL,10,Fclub. I will always support it," he
OL,11,Ftold Salah: Farewell to the King, an
OL,12,FLFC Orginal film made available on
OL,13,FYouTube.
OL,15,F"It means to me everything. You live
OL,16,Fin the club, you feel the love and
OL,17,Fappreciation from the fans.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
