OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779696396
OL,3,CMohamed Salah says he will always love
OL,4,CLiverpool as nine-year story nears an
OL,5,Cend
OL,7,F"This is the most important thing,
OL,8,Fpeople appreciate what you have done
OL,9,Fand appreciate everything you've done
OL,10,Ffor them and for yourself.
OL,12,F"It feels special. I'm blessed. Not
OL,13,Ftoo many people had the opportunity to
OL,14,Fplay here nine years and perform how I
OL,15,Fperformed or just enjoy or go through
OL,16,Fthe process that I've been through.
OL,18,F"So, it's a blessing and something I
OL,19,Fdon't take for granted."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU{D@XO]
